        <section class="intro">
            <h2>Welcome</h2>
            <p>Hi, I’m Quester, a UK-based creative soul who started out in broadcast journalism and ended up exploring a world of stories—written, spoken, visual, and interactive. I have an inquisitive mind, a love for speculative foreign affairs, time-travel theories, ASCII art, and a nostalgic longing for the internet cultures of the mid-2000s.</p>
            <p>I juggle ADHD, which means I often leap from idea to idea, yet I channel that energy into unique, off-beat projects. Through this site, I share my journey—from media experiments and political commentary to surreal art and personal reflections. Consider this my evolving, interactive portfolio-meets-journal, a digital space to connect, reflect, and imagine.</p>
